item.title: Privacy Preserving Machine Learning Research at Imperial College London
item.description: I am working as part of Undergraduate Research Opportunities Program (UROP) at the Information Processing and Communications Lab at Imperial College London. Privacy Aware Sharing in Smart Grids In the new generation electricity supply networks, smart meters play a key role in recording the electricity consumption of a household by reporting it to the utility provider in real-time. However, this real-time information also carries sensitive personal information about the userâ€™s activities.
